[[iftags +版式]]
[[module CSS]]
@import url("https://bhl.scpwikicn.com/css/min/normalize.min.css");
@import url("https://bhl.scpwikicn.com/css/min/black-highlighter.min.css");
[[/module]]
[[/iftags]]

[[include :scp-wiki:component:toggle-sidebar-bhl]]
[[include :scp-wiki:component:centered-header-bhl]]
[[include :etinjat:typeface-cn
|Huiwen-mincho=true
]]

[[module CSS]]

@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Protest+Revolution&display=swap');
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fredericka+the+Great&display=swap');

:root:lang(cn) {
    /* ACT-SPECIFIC CSS */
    --head-prelude: "良秀的提案";
    --head-1: "野兽之径";
    --head-2: "剑刃之路";
    --head-3: "地狱之途";

    --sub-prelude: "地 狱 变";
    --sub-1: "良秀的提案";
    --sub-2: "良秀的提案";
    --sub-3: "良秀的提案";

    /* REGULAR STUFF */

    /* General */

    --bright-accent: 130, 0, 0;
    --medium-accent: 100, 0, 0;
    --dark-accent: 70, 0, 0;

    --background-gradient-color: 255, 220, 220;

    /* Header */

    --header-h1-font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 5vw, 2.8125rem);

    --logo-image: url("");

    --header-title: "良秀的提案";
    --header-title: var(--head-{$act});

    --header-subtitle: var(--sub-prelude);
    --header-subtitle: var(--sub-{$act});

    --header-gradient-color-bottom: 100, 0, 0;
    --header-gradient-color-middle: 10, 0, 0;
    --header-gradient-color-top: 0, 00, 0;

    --swatch-topmenu-bg-color: 30, 10, 10;
    --swatch-topmenu-border-color: 150, 0, 0;

    --diagonal-stripes: unset;
    --header-font: 'Huiwen-mincho', sans-serif;
}

#license-area {
    background-color: rgb(30, 10, 10);
}

#breadcrumbs {
    margin: auto;
}

#header div[class*="top-bar"] > ul > li > ul {
    background: rgba(30, 10, 10, 0.9);
}

#container {
    background: url(https://scptestwiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/sigma%3Aashes-to-ashes-theme/fire.png);
    background-position-x: 0%;
    background-position-y: 0%;
    background-repeat: repeat;
    background-size: auto;
    background-repeat: repeat-x;
    background-position: top center;
    background-size: inherit;
}

#content-wrap::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-image: url(https://scptestwiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/sigma%3Aashes-to-ashes-theme/bamboo.png);
    z-index: -1;
    opacity: 0.05;
    background-position: center center;
}

#content-wrap::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    z-index: -2;
    background-image: url(https://scptestwiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/sigma%3Aashes-to-ashes-theme/parchment.jpg);
    background-position: center center;
    background-size: cover;
    opacity: 0.12;
}

#header::before {
    filter: drop-shadow(0px 3px 2px black);
}

#header div[class*="top-bar"] > ul {
    font-family: var(--header-font);
}

#page-title {
    display: none;
}

#main-content hr {
    border-top: 0.163rem solid rgb(70, 0, 0);
}

:is(div.image-block, div.scp-image-block) {
    gap: 0px;
    border: 5px solid rgba(30, 10, 10, 0.9);
}

:is(div.image-block, div.scp-image-block) :is(.image-caption, .scp-image-caption) {
    background-color: rgba(30, 10, 10, 0.9);
    padding: calc(0.5ex + .0625rem) 0.5ch 0ex;
    color: white;
}

:is(blockquote, .blockquote, div.blockquote, [class*="blockquote"]) {
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 .0625rem rgba(150, 100, 100, .5),inset .0625rem 0 0 0 rgba(150, 100, 100, .5),inset 0 -.0625rem 0 0 rgba(150, 100, 100, .75);
}

[[/module]]
[[iftags +版式]]
[[=]]
[[module Rate]]
[[/=]]

> 噢，是的，正是如此：为了画出这一幅场景，那样的骇人之事发生了。若非如此，即便是伟大的良秀，又怎么可能将地狱的苦难描绘得如此栩栩如生呢？为了完成这张屏风上的画，他的生命也遭葬送，这正是他残酷的命运。
> 
> 可以说，良秀画中的地狱，正是这位天下第一画师本人，终有一天要堕入的地狱啊。

